OL,3,CUUP leader defends Swann's move to
OL,4,Cstep down as health minister
OL,6,FUlster Unionist Party leader Doug
OL,7,FBeattie has defended appointing Robin
OL,8,FSwann as Health Minister, despite
OL,9,Fconfirmation he will stand-down ahead
OL,10,Fof the General Election campaign.
OL,12,FMr Swann had declared himself a
OL,13,FWestminster candidate before
OL,14,FStormont's return in February.
OL,16,FHealth unions say that they are
OL,17,Fdisappointed that he is going to stand
OL,18,Fdown to run in the election.
