OL,3,CUUP leader defends Swann's move to
OL,4,Cstep down as health minister
OL,6,FNorthern Ireland's health service is
OL,7,Fin crisis with the longest waiting
OL,8,Flists in all of the UK.
OL,10,FThe UUP leader said succession
OL,11,Fplanning is already in place and the
OL,12,Fchange would be "seamless". He said he
OL,13,Fcould not say when Mr Swann would
OL,14,Fdepart his office, given an election
OL,15,Fis yet to be called.
