OL,3,CUUP leader defends Swann's move to
OL,4,Cstep down as health minister
OL,6,FMr Beattie said: "The simple fact is
OL,7,Fthis, every other party refused to
OL,8,Ftake health. And it was left to the
OL,9,FUlster Unionist Party, the smallest
OL,10,Fparty in the Executive to stand up and
OL,11,Ftake health.
OL,13,F"We needed to hit the ground running.
OL,14,Fand we hit the ground running by me
OL,15,Fputting in Robin Swann who know the
OL,16,Fbrief, knew the personalities. But I
OL,17,Fhad already announced him as a
OL,18,Fcandidate in South Antrim. He is
OL,19,Frunning in South Antrim, I don't think
OL,20,Fhe could do two."
