OL,3,CUUP leader defends Swann's move to
OL,4,Cstep down as health minister
OL,6,FEarlier this month, the UUP announced
OL,7,FMike Nesbitt would become Assembly
OL,8,FPrivate Secretary to the Health
OL,9,FMinister.
OL,11,FMr Beattie said Mr Nesbitt was
OL,12,Fshadowing the minister, "so that when
OL,13,Fthat transition comes, it is
OL,14,Fabsolutely seamless."
OL,16,F"It makes perfect sense to me - it is
OL,17,Fcalled succession planning.
