OL,3,CUUP leader defends Swann's move to
OL,4,Cstep down as health minister
OL,6,FThere is no difference in what robin
OL,7,Fis doing now to what his successor
OL,8,Fwill be doing. Because the health
OL,9,Fservice's priorities are the health
OL,10,Fminister's priorities, are the Ulster
OL,11,FUnionist Party's priorities.
OL,13,F"Being health minister is not about
OL,14,Fpersonalities, it is about policy."
